Class DataField<T>

java.lang.Object
  com.orm.androrm.DataField<T>
Type Parameters:
T - The Java data type this field represents.
All Implemented Interfaces:
DatabaseField<T>
Direct Known Subclasses:
BooleanField, CharField, DateField, DoubleField, ForeignKeyField, IntegerField
public abstract class DataField<T>
extends Object
implements DatabaseField<T>

This class is the superclass for all database fields, that need a real field in the database. This for example is a IntegerField field, but not a OneToManyField.

Author:
Philipp Giese
